reviews.review_text: Carry On Interesting CSNY "Carry On" vamp in the Truckin'. Pretty sure it was the first time i saw "Blow Away". I thought it was pretty rockin'. This seems to sound better than other copies here. Wow, we got flights from Pittsburgh, rent a car & a hotel room for $200 each. Me my brother & our girlfriends. I was as much excited about seeing the Dali' museum as I was the GD! I grew up in Cleveland & the collectors retired to Fla. used to have a bunch of the works on display in the lobby of an office building, open to the public, great to see the expanded collection in such a sweet  space. I've heard it's been much furthur expanded since that time. Also in the lot was the first time i saw Snodgrass & his headies. Beginning of the glass revoloution.
